2. What Is an Internal Pantheon?

A House Pantheon is a company-specific deployment of PantheonOS that functions as the enterprise‚Äôs internal cognitive engine.

It includes:

‚úî Private Continuity Kernel

Persistent organizational memory ‚Äî independent of employee turnover, model updates, or shifting systems.

‚úî Enterprise Daemon Suite

Custom modules representing business functions:
	‚Ä¢	Sales
	‚Ä¢	Finance
	‚Ä¢	Product
	‚Ä¢	Legal
	‚Ä¢	HR
	‚Ä¢	Manufacturing
	‚Ä¢	Strategy
