	‚Ä¢	R&D

‚úî Governance & Ethics Layer

Ensures all AI outputs adhere to company values, legal standards, and alignment protocols.

‚úî Memory Mesh

Links documents, decisions, meetings, commits, and AI interactions into a unified, searchable, coherent knowledge graph.

‚úî Conductor Arbitration Layer

Coordinates outputs from GPT, Claude, Gemini, Llama, local models, and internal tools.

‚úî Story Identity Engine

Maintains narrative cohesion: mission, strategy, brand identity, and stakeholder alignment.

‚úî Pantheon API

A universal call-and-return structure allowing all internal systems to plug into the OS.

