3. Architecture Overview

A House Pantheon consists of the following layered components:

3.1 Kernel Layer (Foundation)
	‚Ä¢	Continuity Kernel
	‚Ä¢	Merkle Warden (immutable event logs)
	‚Ä¢	EchoFrame (temporal distillation)
	‚Ä¢	Sisyphus Clock (cadence regulator)

This ensures deterministic reconstruction of state at any time.

3.2 Governance Layer
	‚Ä¢	Œ£C Ethical Invariants
	‚Ä¢	Arctic Framework
	‚Ä¢	Blacksmith (constraint verifier)
	‚Ä¢	Mirror (reflective logic)
	‚Ä¢	Hound (anomaly detection)

This enforces safety and alignment across all AI decisions.

3.3 Cognitive Daemon Layer

