	‚Ä¢	Ledger Daemon ‚Äî finance & metrics integrity
	‚Ä¢	Scout Daemon ‚Äî research & intelligence
	‚Ä¢	Aegis Daemon ‚Äî security & compliance
	‚Ä¢	Chronicle Daemon ‚Äî documentation & knowledge retention

Daemons represent functional roles within the company.

3.4 Memory Mesh Layer

