This forms a semantic lattice with Pantheon continuity.

3.5 Orchestration Layer
	‚Ä¢	Conductor (decision arbitration)
	‚Ä¢	Protocol Bridges (API connectors)
	‚Ä¢	Multi-model routing (GPT ‚Üî Claude ‚Üî Gemini ‚Üî Internal Models)

This layer ensures cross-model coherence.

3.6 Presentation Layer
	‚Ä¢	LLM assistants
	‚Ä¢	Dashboards
	‚Ä¢	Decision briefs
	‚Ä¢	Internal copilots
	‚Ä¢	Departmental UIs

